      <h2>7. Kärcher WD 5 P 25L Stainless Steel — Best for Fine Dust (4.6★)</h2>
      <p><strong>ASIN:</strong> B09MD77LKP</p>
      <p>The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09MD77LKP?tag=sciencesolved-20" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank">Kärcher WD 5 P V-25/5/22</a> brings German engineering to jobsite cleanup. With a 25-liter (6.6-gallon) stainless steel tank, 240 AW suction power, and a pleated filter designed for fine dust, this vac excels at precision cleaning on finishing sites. The stainless steel tank is more durable than poly and easier to clean after wet pickup.</p>
