      <h2>How to Choose Based on Your Trade</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Framers & Rough Carpenters:</strong> Prioritize tank size and HP. The DEWALT DXV16PA (16 Gal, 6.5 HP) or STANLEY 10 Gallon (6 HP) handle heavy construction debris without constant emptying.</li>
        <li><strong>Finish Carpenters & Cabinet Installers:</strong> Quiet operation and fine-dust filtration matter most. The DEWALT 10 Gal STEALTHSONIC or Kärcher WD 5 P are top picks.</li>
        <li><strong>Electricians & Plumbers:</strong> Portability is key. The DEWALT DXV06P (6 Gal, 4.7★) or DEWALT 6 Gal STEALTHSONIC are lightweight enough to carry on a shoulder strap.</li>
        <li><strong>Remodelers:</strong> You need a versatile all-around vac. The DEWALT 9 Gal DXV09PZ or STANLEY 10 Gal handle mixed debris and fit in a van.</li>
        <li><strong>HVAC & Service Techs:</strong> Compact and quiet. The DEWALT 6 Gal STEALTHSONIC or Kärcher WD 2 Plus are easy to carry through homes and apartments.</li>
        <li><strong>General Contractors:</strong> The DEWALT DXV16PA is the workhorse for crew-size job sites. Pair it with a smaller portable vac for detail work.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What About Noise? A Practical Note</h2>
      <p>Standard shop vacs operate at 85–90 dB — equivalent to heavy traffic, and loud enough to require hearing protection under OSHA guidelines. If your crew is running a vac all day, the noise adds up.</p>
      <p>DEWALT's STEALTHSONIC technology reduces noise levels significantly, making conversation possible and reducing crew fatigue. For remodelers working in occupied homes, a quiet vac can be the difference between a happy client and a complaint. Both the 10-gallon and 6-gallon STEALTHSONIC models deliver this advantage without sacrificing suction power.</p>

      <h2>Final Verdict</h2>
      <p>For most contractors, the <strong>DEWALT 9 Gallon DXV09PZ</strong> (4.6★) or the <strong>STANLEY 10 Gallon</strong> (4.5★) offer the best balance of capacity, power, and value. If you need maximum portability, the <strong>DEWALT DXV06P</strong> (4.7★) is the top-rated compact option. For quiet operation in occupied spaces, the <strong>DEWALT 10 Gal STEALTHSONIC</strong> (4.6★) is in a class of its own.</p>
      <p>Whatever you choose, a quality shop vac is one of the highest-ROI investments on any job site — it speeds cleanup, reduces dust hazards, and keeps your work area professional and safe.</p>

